{"id":1735026,"retrievedAt":"2026-07-21T12:47:12.215Z","response":{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/vgPdRKSYaFOGZdO8M446lYwyxJ.jpg","belongs_to_collection":null,"budget":0,"genres":[],"homepage":"","id":1735026,"imdb_id":null,"origin_country":["IT"],"original_language":"it","original_title":"Puca","overview":"It is the early afternoon of a summer day in the 1990s. While their parents are asleep, Lotti and Malibù (nicknames the sisters use for each other) decide to sneak out to a local bar—a spot frequented by the boy they both have a crush on. Puca, the youngest, insists on coming along, threatening to wake their parents with her screaming if they refuse. The three girls set off; as they pass the beach, Puca wanders toward the water’s edge and claims to have seen a mermaid. Once at the bar, the older sisters—preoccupied with their adolescent moods—lose sight of Puca. A search ensues, leading to a confrontation that clears the air between them, followed by a fleeting glimpse of the mermaid diving and vanishing beneath the waves; that image makes them realize their childhood is gone forever. The unexpected happens when they return home to alert their parents…","popularity":0.0071,"poster_path":null,"production_companies":[{"id":150853,"logo_path":null,"name":"GM Productions","origin_country":""},{"id":207594,"logo_path":null,"name":"Limbo film","origin_country":""},{"id":227967,"logo_path":null,"name":"Hubris Pictures","origin_country":""},{"id":305087,"logo_path":null,"name":"Red Couch Pictures","origin_country":""},{"id":305088,"logo_path":null,"name":"Eidos Film","origin_country":""}],"production_countries":[{"iso_3166_1":"IT","name":"Italy"}],"release_date":"","revenue":0,"runtime":14,"softcore":false,"spoken_languages":[{"english_name":"Italian","iso_639_1":"it","name":"Italiano"}],"status":"Released","tagline":"","title":"Puca","video":false,"vote_average":0,"vote_count":0,"alternative_titles":{"titles":[]},"credits":{"cast":[{"adult":false,"gender":0,"id":636062